data.description: ***With acceptable offer, Sellers are offering up to $10,000 in an allowance/concessions.*** Construction completed March 2023, this home is now available! The owners relocated due to a new job, which came shortly after they moved in. Step inside from the covered front porch to a welcoming formal dining room, seamlessly connecting to the kitchen and living room. The kitchen, featuring an island, boasts granite counters, a pantry, breakfast nook, and a bay window. Stay cozy in the living room with a fireplace for colder months. Upstairs, discover all bedrooms and the guest bathroom, along with a convenient laundry room. The primary bedroom impresses with an ensuite bathroom, complete with a double vanity, garden tub, separate shower, and a walk-in closet. Positioned for convenience to Fort Liberty (Bragg) and just 1 hour and 15 minutes from RDU. Don't miss this opportunity--schedule a showing with your REALTOR(r) today and make this home yours!
